          <div class="check-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>Patients with <strong>inflammatory joint conditions</strong> — arthritis, bursitis, tendinopathy — across the shoulder, elbow, wrist, knee, hip and spine</span></div>
          <div class="check-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>Oncology patients requiring <strong>musculoskeletal pain support</strong> alongside their primary cancer treatment</span></div>
          <div class="check-item"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span><strong>Vegetarians and vegans</strong> with unexplained chronic pain that may be linked to B12 or D3 deficiency</span></div>
